<scriptment id="83000" point="clarisse_act" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-11-02" status="final">
	<part>
		<comment>Sporadic event occurs between 2011-11-02 and 2011-11-03.</comment>
		<condition>
			<comment>The Player hired Clarisse Bernadette.</comment>
			<narration>In the Cardboard City, Clarisse runs to Soleil and jumps up and down!</narration>
			<line id="1000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Soleil, Soleil! I'm an Actress!</line>
			<line id="2000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">A Real Actress!</line>
			<narration>Soleil laughs.</narration>
			<line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">It comforts me now to what makes an Actress.</line>
			<line id="4000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">So you got That Acting Job? When do you start?</line>
			<line id="5000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Yesterday!</line>
			<line id="6000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Have you gone?</line>
			<line id="7000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">No!</line>
			<line id="8000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Why bother? They'll reject me like everyone else.</line>
			<narration>Soleil raises a finger.</narration>
			<line id="9000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">They'll leave me like all the others.</line>
			<line id="10000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">I'll once again be jobless; They'll just lay me off.</line>
			<condition>
				<choice number="1">
					<line id="11000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Sega hasn't laid you off.</line>
					<line id="12000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Sega is going bankrupt.</line>
				</choice>
				<choice number="2">
					<line id="13000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">So you'll tell everyone you're an Actress, without being an Actress?</line>
					<line id="14000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">That's the plan! It's safe, it's sensical,</line>
					<line id="15000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">It's stupid.</line>
				</choice>
			</condition>
			<narration>Soleil puts her hand on Clarisse's shoulder. She stares her down.</narration>
			<line id="16000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Become an Actress, or you will never be called one.</line>
			<narration>Clarisse sighs.</narration>
			<line id="17000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">I'll have to put less time into work.</line>
			<comment>Clarisse's Base Ambition decreases sharply.</comment>
		</condition>
	</part>
</scriptment>